    "description_long": "This is a single bed with a light wood frame featuring a built-in storage unit at the head, which appears to function as a shelf or cabinet. The bed has a checkered mattress in shades of red, white, and gray, which sits atop a solid platform base. Two drawers with metallic handles are integrated into the lower section of the frame, providing additional storage space. The headboard is tall and boxy, while the side panel curves gently for added style and support. The overall construction suggests a sturdy, practical design suitable for compact urban living spaces.",
